/* eslint-disable max-len */
import isEmpty from 'lodash/isEmpty';
import isNull from 'lodash/isNull';
import isBoolean from 'lodash/isBoolean';
import startCase from 'lodash/startCase';
import get from 'lodash/get';
import { notification } from 'antd';
import { isSurfaceEnquiry } from 'common-util/product/enquiry/functions';
import { hasZeroError } from '../ChargesTable/helpers';
 
/* for error initialization check: store/vendor/quotes/helpers */
 
const ERROR_MESSAGE = {
	carrier: 'Shipping line is required',
	charges: 'Charges is incomplete',
	valid_till: 'Validity date is required',
	transit_time: 'Transit time is required',
	sailingSchedule: 'Sailing schedule is required',
	detentionFreeTimeAtDestination: 'Detention time is required',
	transportTransitTime: 'Transport transit time is required',
	transShip: 'Transshipment port is required',
	/* custom */
	ceilingRateExceeded: 'Freight charges greater than acceptable value',
	slabRateExceeded: 'Please Reduce the cost at least by given Cost Reduction Rate',
	/* check if any error is left */
	any: 'Some fields or charges missing',
};
 
export const SHOW_NOTIFICATION = errorArray => {
	notification.error({
		message: 'Fill the details:',
		description: errorArray,
		duration: 10,
		placement: 'bottomLeft',
		style: {
			width: 480,
		},
	});
};
 
const checkIfAnyChargesError = (errorValues, chargeList = {}) => {
	const errorList = [];
	let existingChargeDisplayName = {};
	Object.keys(errorValues || {}).forEach((errorKey = '') => {
		const errorProp = errorValues[errorKey];
		(Object.entries(errorProp) || []).forEach(([key, value]) => {
			const chargeDisplayName = chargeList[errorKey]?.[key]?.display_name?.toLowerCase();
			if (chargeDisplayName && existingChargeDisplayName[chargeDisplayName]) {
				errorList.push({ chargeDisplayName });
			} else {
				existingChargeDisplayName[chargeDisplayName] = true;
			}
			errorList.push(Object.values(value).some(error => error));
		});
		existingChargeDisplayName = {};
	});
 
	return errorList.filter(error => error);
};
 
const hasCustomOrDefaultErrors = errorValues => {
	const values = Object.values(errorValues);
	return values.some(error => error);
};
 
export const CHECK_ERROR = ({
	formError, enquiry, quote, otherParams, formRequisites,
}) => {
	const { need_transport_transit_time: needTransTransitTime } = otherParams || {};
	const { ceiling_rate, slab_rate } = enquiry || {};
	const { total_per_unit } = get(quote, 'total_charges.11_freight_charges.sub_total', {});
	const { total, original_total } = get(quote, 'total_charges.total', {});
	const { status } = quote || {};
	const errorObject = { ...(formError || {}) };
	const chargesErrorList = [];
 
	if (isSurfaceEnquiry(enquiry)) {
		/* for surface enquiry, carrier & sailing-schedule is not required, hence false. */
		errorObject.carrier = false;
		errorObject.sailingSchedule = false;
	} else {
		if (isNull(quote.carrier)) {
			errorObject.carrier = true;
		} else {
			/* other carrier is select & carrier_name is not added */
			errorObject.carrier = (quote.carrier || {}).code === 'OTHR' && !quote.other_carrier_name;
		}
 
		errorObject.sailingSchedule = Object.values(quote.schedule).every(
			eachSchedule => !eachSchedule,
		);
	}
 
	/* throw error, if ceiling rate is exceeded */
	errorObject.ceilingRateExceeded = ceiling_rate ? !(total_per_unit <= ceiling_rate) : false;
 
	/* throw error, if quote total cost is not decreased by slab rate */
	const total_difference = original_total - total;
	errorObject.slabRateExceeded =		!(status === 'draft') && (total < original_total && total_difference < slab_rate);
 
	errorObject.transShip = quote.trans_ship_present && isEmpty(quote.trans_ship);
	errorObject.transportTransitTime = needTransTransitTime && isNull(quote.transport_transit_time);
 
	(Object.keys(quote.charges_list) || []).forEach((chargeLocation = '') => {
		const list = quote.charges_list[chargeLocation]; // each charge location's charge type
		errorObject.charges[chargeLocation] = {};
 
		const existingCharges = Object.keys(list || {}).map(key => ({
			chargeKey: key,
			chargeName: list[key].display_name?.toLowerCase(),
		}));
 
		Object.keys(list || {}).forEach(chargeType => {
			if (chargeType !== 'display_name' && typeof list[chargeType] === 'object') {
				errorObject.charges[chargeLocation][chargeType] = {};
				errorObject.charges[chargeLocation][chargeType].isDisplayNameInvalid = false;
 
				if (list[chargeType].is_custom_field) {
					/* Custom charge! */
 
					const isExistingCharge = existingCharges
						.map(
							({ chargeKey, chargeName }) => chargeName === list[chargeType].display_name?.toLowerCase()
								&& chargeKey !== chargeType,
						)
						.includes(true);
 
					if (
						(list[chargeType].display_name && list[chargeType].price)
						|| (!list[chargeType].display_name && !list[chargeType].price)
					) {
						/* if (display_name && price) is empty OR (display_name && price) is present => good */
						errorObject.charges[chargeLocation][chargeType].isPriceInvalid = false;
						chargesErrorList.push(false);
 
						// If added Charge already exists then show Error
						if (isExistingCharge) {
							errorObject.charges[chargeLocation][chargeType].isDisplayNameInvalid = true;
							chargesErrorList.push(true);
						}
					} else {
						/* either display_name or price is missing! */
						if (!list[chargeType].display_name) {
							errorObject.charges[chargeLocation][chargeType].isDisplayNameInvalid = true;
						} else if (list[chargeType].price === '' || isNull(list[chargeType].price)) {
							errorObject.charges[chargeLocation][chargeType].isPriceInvalid = true;
							if (isExistingCharge) {
								errorObject.charges[chargeLocation][chargeType].isDisplayNameInvalid = true;
							}
						}
						chargesErrorList.push(true);
					}
				} else if (list[chargeType].required && !list[chargeType].price) {
					/* if charge_type is required and price is NOT valid */
					errorObject.charges[chargeLocation][chargeType].isPriceInvalid = true;
					chargesErrorList.push(true);
				} else if (hasZeroError(list[chargeType].non_zero, list[chargeType].price)) {
					/* if zero_is_not_allowed and price 0 (basically, 0 is not allowed)
					and it can be required or maybe not required */
					errorObject.charges[chargeLocation][chargeType].isPriceInvalid = true;
					chargesErrorList.push(true);
				} else {
					errorObject.charges[chargeLocation][chargeType].isPriceInvalid = false;
					chargesErrorList.push(false);
				}
			}
		});
	});
 
	/* custom column checks */
	(quote.custom_columns || []).forEach(({ name, value, required }) => {
		if (required) {
			errorObject.customColumns[name] = !value;
		}
	});
 
	/* quote default checks */
	get(formRequisites, 'quote_default_columns.quote_columns', []).forEach(
		({ key, filled, mandatory }) => {
			if (mandatory && !filled) {
				errorObject.quoteDefaults[key] = quote[key] === 0 ? false : !quote[key];
			}
		},
	);
 
	const errorCopy = { ...errorObject };
	delete errorCopy.customColumns;
	delete errorCopy.quoteDefaults;
	delete errorCopy.charges;
	delete errorCopy.any;
 
	const checkFields = (Object.values(errorCopy) || []).some(error => error);
	const checkCharges = (chargesErrorList || []).some(error => error);
	const checkCustom = (Object.values(errorObject.customColumns) || []).some(error => error);
	const checkQuoteDefault = (Object.values(errorObject.quoteDefaults) || []).some(error => error);
 
	/* if has error, errorObject.any = true! */
	errorObject.any = checkFields || checkCharges || checkCustom || checkQuoteDefault;
	return errorObject;
};
 
export const SHOW_ERROR_NOTIFICATION = (errors, isAir, quote) => {
	const errorArray = [];
 
	Object.entries(errors || {}).forEach(([errorKey, errorValue]) => {
		if (errorKey !== 'charges' && errorKey !== 'customColumns' && errorKey !== 'quoteDefaults') {
			if (isBoolean(errorValue) && errorValue) {
				if (errorKey === 'any') {
					if (errorArray.length === 0) {
						errorArray.push(<p key={errorKey}>{ERROR_MESSAGE[errorKey]}</p>);
					}
				} else {
					errorArray.push(
						<p key={`error-${errorKey}`}>
							{errorKey === 'carrier' && isAir ? 'Air line is required' : ERROR_MESSAGE[errorKey]}
						</p>,
					);
				}
			}
		} else if (errorKey === 'charges') {
			const chargesErrors = checkIfAnyChargesError(errorValue, quote.charges_list);
			const existingChargeErrorList = chargesErrors.filter(
				chargeError => chargeError.chargeDisplayName,
			);
 
			errorArray.push(<p key={errorKey}> {ERROR_MESSAGE[errorKey]} </p>);
			existingChargeErrorList.forEach(existingChargeError => errorArray.push(
				<p key={`${errorKey}-existing-charge`}>
					<strong>{existingChargeError.chargeDisplayName.titleize()}</strong> already exists!
				</p>,
			));
		} else if (
			(errorKey === 'customColumns' || errorKey === 'quoteDefaults')
			&& hasCustomOrDefaultErrors(errorValue)
		) {
			(Object.keys(errorValue) || []).forEach(value => {
				if (errorValue && errorValue[value]) {
					errorArray.push(<p key={`error-${value}`}>{startCase(value)} is required</p>);
				}
			});
		}
	});
 
	if (errorArray.length !== 0) {
		SHOW_NOTIFICATION(errorArray);
	}
 
	return null;
};
 
export const SHOW_EXISTING_CHARGE_NOTIFICATION = existingCharge => {
	notification.error({
		message: [
			<p>
				<strong>{existingCharge}</strong> already exists!
			</p>,
		],
		duration: 10,
		placement: 'bottomLeft',
		style: {
			width: 480,
		},
	});
};
